node.text:
Hey family  i want to share something with you very special!!!! In a time when the world is experiencing so much sadness...my little 5yr.
Old  friend  Riot Copeland took time out of her Precious  Innocent day Of being at little girl, Who should not have to see and hear about all of the  Badness going on in the world today Along with her parents To drop a beautiful letter and a $50 donation WOW!!! It's obvious  That  Her parents are just as beautiful as she is , in teaching  her  no matter what color our skin tone is we are all one people. Thank you mom and dad for raising such a Good person..
